snippet.title: Skate City – Available Now Exclusively On Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
Skate City:  https://www.skatecitygame.com
Find it on Apple Arcade: https://apple.co/-SkateCity

What once seemed like a concrete jungle will soon become your playground…Skate City is now available, exclusively on Apple Arcade.

Trailer by Joe Pease
Music by Granbar
